  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The cement with a Clorox paste, with my finger, I was pasting to look white.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And because I did that, I didn't have to go out to do when was every day the selection.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They-- Mengele and Margot [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Grazer ?] were selecting 50, 60, 100 person for their-- I know now for what.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At the time, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For the experiment, what Germans, they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And with that, that Miri-- took me to clean that chimney, I was saved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because I was extremely white, blonde, and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Probably, I would have been the first who Mengele would select.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Sometimes-- I know now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At the time, I didn't-- the blood was taken out from the selected people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when they couldn't move, they didn't have any more blood, they were just thrown to the [? crematorium, ?] just was left to die that way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I was doing that every single day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because I did that, I didn't have to go out, 3:00 in the morning, when everybody was always started to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I just had to go out in my line, where there was five of us, my two cousins and their two cousins.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Which happened to be, later on, my two sister, older sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "One of the sister is still alive, is about my mother's age in Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was very tall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't grow since then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since-- actually, I shrink already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was about 12, maybe only 11 and a 1/2.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as soon I drink that three-- swallow-- I swallowed the three swallowing food, stop my menstruation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I-- exactly I had, at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think-- I don't know what was in the food, but somehow made us not to think anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
